sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant BrowseController
    participant PlaybackController
    participant PlaybackService
    participant UserController
    participant DB as SQLite DB

    %% Browse
    User->>Browser: Visit /browse/
    Browser->>BrowseController: GET /browse/
    BrowseController->>DB: Song.filter(is_public=True, status=SUCCESS).order_by(-created_at)
    BrowseController-->>Browser: Render browse/index.html with songs

    alt Search query entered
        User->>Browser: Type search query
        Browser->>BrowseController: GET /browse/?q=query
        BrowseController->>DB: Song.filter(is_public=True, status=SUCCESS, title__icontains=query)
        BrowseController-->>Browser: Render filtered song list
    end

    %% Playback
    User->>Browser: Click play on a song
    Browser->>PlaybackController: GET /playback/play/<song_id>/
    PlaybackController->>PlaybackService: get_song_playback_info(song_id)
    PlaybackService->>DB: Song.objects.get(id=song_id)
    PlaybackService-->>PlaybackController: { song_id, title, audio_url, duration_seconds, status }
    PlaybackController-->>Browser: JSON { playback metadata }
    Browser->>User: Audio player loads and plays song

    %% Credit Balance Check
    User->>Browser: View credit balance (Creator only)
    Browser->>UserController: GET /user/balance/<creator_id>/
    UserController->>DB: Aggregate CreditTransactions (ADD - DEDUCT + REFUND)
    UserController-->>Browser: JSON { creator_name, credit_balance }
